            I ſhould alſo vſe a word of Exhortation to my brethren of the Miniſtery: the more holy and reuerent our Calling is, the more it concerneth vs to looke that wee walke worthy thereof, and to beware leſt wee diſhonour it by our words or deeds. My brethren, it is not for vs to bee deſpiſers of thoſe which follow holineſſe; for our doctrine teacheth vs, and all others, to bee holy;

