                  Matth. 7. 23. 
               Away from me, ye workers of iniquitie.
            
            Therefore to conclude, the Lord giue vs all grace ſo to demeane our ſelues in our places, that his Name may be glorified by vs, his Church edified, and our reuerend Calling adorned, that our prayers may be accepted of the Lord, and our bleſſing of the people may, with this Prieſtly benediction, goe vp vnto his holy dwelling Place, euen vnto heauen▪ which he grant for his infinite mercies ſake in Chriſt▪ to whom, with the Father and the holy Ghoſt, be aſcribed all praiſe and glorie now and for euer.
            Amen.
            FINIS.
            
         
      
   

